    "stdyInfo": {
      "abstract": [
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "fr",
          "value": "Le but de cette étude cas-témoins en population était de comparer les variables de santé bucco-dentaire (quantité de plaque, le tartre, gingivite, et la fonction masticatoire) entre les patients traités par pression positive continue CPAP / BiPAP et les sujets témoins"
        },
        {
          "contentType": "purpose",
          "lang": "en",
          "value": "The aim of this population-based, case-control study was to compare oral health variables (amount of plaque, tartar, gingivitis and masticatory function) between patients treated by continuous positive airway pressure (CPAP/BiPAP) and control subjects."
        }
      ],
